detail.name: Dr. Brief
detail.effect: [On Play] Look at 7 cards from the top of your deck, reveal up to 1 Extra with a cost of 2 or less and add it to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom of their owner's deck in a random order.

detail.name: ブリーフ博士
detail.effect: 【登場時】自分のデッキの上から7枚を見て、コスト2以下のエクストラ1枚までを公開し、手札に加える。残りをランダムにデッキの下に置く。
